title: Dell PowerVault ME5: Pools
agents: dell_powervault_me5
catalog: hw/storagehw/dell
license: GPLv2
distribution: Sher Zaman
description:
 Monitors the capacity of each Dell PowerVault ME5 virtual pool. The pool is
 presented like a filesystem, so the standard Checkmk "Filesystem (used space
 and growth)" ruleset applies, including used-space levels, the magic factor
 and trend computation (default 80%/90%).

 Over-commit and pool health are shown as informational text; over-commit is
 expected on thin-provisioned pools.

item:
 The pool name (for example {"A"}).

discovery:
 One service is created per pool.
